{"tid":790521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[金融行業巴絲入]加拿大求職難？","createTime":"2018-08-23T05:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T09:59:10.000Z","uid":109571,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6da8a1668406b0372ad7a28bfb3814e43279ec","tid":790521,"uid":109571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"希望各位加拿大巴絲賜教<br />\n小弟係金融行業bo/mo打滾左就黎2年，唔outstanding，<br />\n近排心思思移民加拿大，計過分有41x，諗住用working holiday攞一年加拿大經驗，咁就掹車邊夠分。<br />\n問題係加拿大本身搵工難，我想搵番finance/banking related 工怕會更難（可能唔係？）人地請個local，train一陣就做到，香港經驗分分鐘冇用<br />\n其實都唔係一定要做番本行，只係冇經驗都唔知做乜好。。。<br />\n有時都諗係咪應該及早轉型做啲用tech多啲既工，只少俾純文職有競爭力啲。。。<br />\n好想係2年內離開香港，希望有加拿大人指點下我，或者等我死左條心<br />\n<br />\nps：有英國護照(唔到冇得揀都唔會去)，唔知搞移民會唔會易啲？"},{"pid":"d120a134627c46e89f2f188becd58b215b9a1664","tid":790521,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"邊度可以計分？"},{"pid":"5680fbdc53b4cc1a4d7ed6534a91e98fef0c8c7d","tid":790521,"uid":109571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d120a134627c46e89f2f188becd58b215b9a1664","tid":790521,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"邊度可以計分？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"唔介意簡體可以用呢個<br />\n<a href=\"http://eoivisa.com/fsw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feoivisa.com%2Ffsw%2F&d=WAyJM2esBSIt0x96w2cgd8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f4b500b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://eoivisa.com/fsw/</a>"},{"pid":"58debfbd8d6f4036417bbb35cfd8cd0587443f37","tid":790521,"uid":109571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"各位想移民既可以係度討論下"},{"pid":"f02fd8072e50419a07deaceddfdc25889099e1d2","tid":790521,"uid":188593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔想去英國？<br />\n利申：咩護照都冇 想去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476fc5fd1809b922d3de9215563701b7d4c83687","tid":